change that is happening within us and without.

14
00:02:13,370 --> 00:02:18,069
         
The whole atmosphere today is governed by

15
00:02:18,069 --> 00:02:22,480
human beings.

16
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:35,330
I don't know how far Paramachaitanya works
it out, but it is for us to open ourselves

17
00:02:35,330 --> 00:02:41,760
