27
00:04:11,769 --> 00:04:20,520
conditions and ego that are lingering still.

28
00:04:20,520 --> 00:04:24,860
Definitely you will drop them.

29
00:04:24,860 --> 00:04:34,580
With your attention, it will run away.

30
00:04:34,580 --> 00:04:44,630
Then you will realize that every day your
attention is getting purified, getting powerful,

31
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:48,710
getting compassionate.

32
00:04:48,710 --> 00:05:02,220
Normally, whatever reaction you have in your
