33
00:05:02,220 --> 00:05:18,540
the whole thing, and your power of attention,
through that witnessing force, acts and it

34
00:05:18,540 --> 00:05:20,050
works.

35
00:05:20,050 --> 00:05:30,810
It works not only on you, but on everything
that surrounds you.

36
00:05:30,810 --> 00:05:35,930
         
Firstly, through your meditation, in that

37
00:05:35,930 --> 00:05:44,270
state of meditation, you expand within yourself.

38
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:48,570
You stay in the present.

39
00:05:48,570 --> 00:05:53,220
The other day, somebody asked Me, "Where was
Your last birthday?"

40
00:05:53,220 --> 00:05:58,900
I just forgot where it was.

41
00:05:58,900 --> 00:06:04,600
Otherwise My memory is very good, like an
elephant.

42
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:08,890
But this I forgot.

43
00:06:08,890 --> 00:06:26,150
Perhaps, every time, every day, you live in
the present, and you grow, so you forget when

44
00:06:26,150 --> 00:06:33,150
