00:06:44,080 --> 00:07:02,410
time I go to a place, I find very nice new
people coming in and some of the horrible

47
00:07:02,410 --> 00:07:07,560
ones from the old lot disappearing.

48
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:20,630
It's something like, when the tree grows,
the leaves go on falling and new leaves start

49
00:07:20,630 --> 00:07:22,570
coming.

