52
00:07:49,530 --> 00:07:52,310
people.

53
00:07:52,310 --> 00:08:05,330
To Me, it's like a miraculous fireworks.

54
00:08:05,330 --> 00:08:17,870
It starts like a small line and then opens
up into several beautiful patterns.

55
00:08:17,870 --> 00:08:32,830
It is impossible to envisage or to visualize
what will happen to us, to Sahaj Yog and to

56
00:08:32,830 --> 00:08:38,650
all of you.

57
00:08:38,650 --> 00:08:52,570
I have never learned to imagine things, but
the vision that you see is really remarkable,

58
00:08:52,570 --> 00:09:07,630
is very remarkable, that I see all Sahaja
