59
00:09:07,630 --> 00:09:25,320
themselves in a very beautiful and very deep
manner.

60
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:42,380
This, when comes in, that really makes your
attention absolutely enwrapped in such divine

61
00:09:42,380 --> 00:09:46,560
bliss that you forget that moment.

62
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:51,050
         
One of those moments are when you celebrate

63
00:09:51,050 --> 00:09:52,950
My Birthday.

